      "intervention": "Use of sacrificial organic interlayer like polystyrene or tpm",
      "comparator": "",
      "primary_outcome": "Successful synthesis of yolk-shell nanoparticle with intact silica shell and detached core",
      "quantitative_target": "",
      "mechanism": "Utilization of sacrificial organic interlayer to define void space and ensure structural integrity during removal",
